data.title: Martin Fitzgerald (Passions)
data.meta_description: Martin Fitzgerald is a fictional character on the NBC/DirecTV daytime drama Passions. Martin was played by Richard Steinmetz from May 14, 2004, to October 3, 2006. William Bumiller had previously played the role in flashbacks from 1999 to 2000.
